Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://passt.top/

Package: passt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: User-mode networking for VMs and containers
 passt implements a translation layer between a Layer-2 network
 interface and native Layer-4 sockets on the host. pasta (Pack
 A Subtle Tap Abstraction) binds tap and socket namespaces for
 rootless container networking. It is the default network mode
 for rootless Podman 5+.
